    Marker interface to generate a solution info for the JVM SDK user agent.

    SphereApiConfig
    Configuration to make request for a platform web service, does not include authentication configuration or tokens.
    SphereAuthConfig
    Contains the configuration to fetch access keys for the commercetools platform.
    SphereAuthConfigBuilder 
    SphereClient
    A client interface to perform requests to the platform.

    The full api and auth configuration for a commercetools client.
    SphereClientConfigBuilder 
    SphereClientDecorator
    A public base class to decorate SphereClients.
    SphereClientFactory
    A factory to instantiate platform Java clients which use CompletionStage as future implementation.
    SphereCorrelationIdConfig 
    SphereHttpClientFactory
    In order to work, the sdk needs an HttpClient provider, this can be done by extending SphereHttpClientFactory and exposing it as a service
